item.title: Confusion and Delay
item.author: mubix
item.description: Due to a PEBKAC error with the ID 10 T, I have had to retype parts 2 and 3, which were ready to go out the door. In the mean time while I fix myself, here are a couple sites that can keep you busy: Search google for exploits: http://www.exploitsearch.com/ Watch just about any TV show (and some movies) online: http://www.surfthechannel.com/ Play any NES game online: http://www.virtualnes.com/ Start a blog without any signup?
